methods.name: ExecuteTick
methods.comment:
@param CurrentThread - thread we are executing on, useful to pass along as new tasks are created
@param MyCompletionGraphEvent - completion event for this task. Useful for holding the completetion of this task until certain child tasks are complete.

methods.name: DiagnosticMessage
methods.comment: Abstract function to describe this tick. Used to print messages about illegal cycles in the dependency graph

properties.name: Target
properties.comment: Buildable that is the target of this tick.
